and Jonathan M. Fisher (FZJ).

Current development team is composed of Zamaan Raza (FZJ), Alexander
Schober (FZJ), Tobias Weber (ILL), Joachim Wuttke (FZJ).

We acknowledge help by our student intern, Janike Katter (FZJ).

